TextEng: A miniature world? How is that possible?
Tiny people live in snowball?
What does this have to do with the Word of Power?
Text: 이게 권능의 언령과 무슨 상관이 있죠?

TextEng: What this got do with Power Word?
Text: 이게 권능의 언령이랑 무슨 상관 있어?

TextEng: How did you manage to get this teleportation scroll? And why did Nax tell you all this?
Text: 어떻게 이 순간이동 두루마리를 구했어요? 그리고 왜 낙스가 이 모든 걸 말해줬죠?

TextEng: How you get teleporty paper? And why Nax tell you all this stuff?
Text: 어떻게 순간이동 종이 구했어? 그리고 왜 낙스가 이 모든 거 말해줬어?

TextEng: How can I get the Word out?
How me get Power Word out?
Okay, get me in!
Me want inside snowball!
Forget it, it sounds too risky.
This be big danger. Me not like.
I'm not here to fill your drink. I'm <FullName>. I work for Aarin Gend.
Text: 당신 술잔을 채우러 온 게 아니에요. 저는 <FullName>입니다. 아린 겐드를 위해 일하죠.

TextEng: Me not here to fill you drink. Me name is <FullName>. Me work for Aarin Gend.
Text: 나 네 술잔 채우러 온 거 아니야. 나 이름은 <FullName>이야. 나 아린 겐드를 위해 일해.

TextEng: I'd like to ask you some questions.
Me want ask you stuff.
I'll be going now.
Me go now.
Where can I find the Words of Power?
Text: 권능의 언령을 어디서 찾을 수 있죠?

TextEng: Tell me about the Creator Race.
How did you end up here in Beorunna's Well?
I need some directions.
Where me find Power Words?
You tell me 'bout Creator Race.
How you end up here in Beorunna's Well?
Me need directions.
I was hoping you could tell me something about this snow globe.
Text: 이 스노 글로브에 대해 뭔가 말해주길 바랬어요.

TextEng: Me hoping you could tell me stuff 'bout this snowball.
Text: 나 이 눈덩이에 대해 뭔가 말해주길 바랬어.

TextEng: I've got the snow globe right here.
Me got snowball right here.
Surely you must know something.
Some expert you turned out to be.
But you gotta know some stuff, right?
You not much of an expert.
Where can I find this Word?
Text: 이 언령을 어디서 찾을 수 있죠?

TextEng: Where Word be? You tell me!
I want to ask you something else.
Me want ask other stuff.
Where can I find the snow globe?
Text: 스노 글로브를 어디서 찾을 수 있죠?

TextEng: Where me find snowball?
If you know where one of the Words of Power is, you'd better tell me. I don't want this to get nasty.
Text: 권능의 언령 중 하나가 어디 있는지 안다면, 말하는 게 좋을 거예요. 안 좋게 가고 싶지 않아요.

TextEng: If you know where Power Word be you tell me! You not want me get mad at you!
Text: 권능의 언령 어디 있는지 알면 말해! 나 화내게 하지 마!

TextEng: Task? What kind of task?
What you task be?
Sounds like the snow globe's important. What else will you give me if I bring it back for you?
Text: 스노 글로브가 중요한 것 같은데요. 돌려드리면 다른 걸 더 주시나요?

TextEng: Sound like snowball be important. What else you give me if me get it back?
Text: 눈덩이가 중요한 것 같아. 내가 돌려주면 다른 거 더 줘?

TextEng: I'll be back when I get that snow globe for you, Lillian!
Text: 스노 글로브를 구하면 다시 올게요, 릴리안!

TextEng: Me be back when me get snowball for you!
Text: 나 네 눈덩이 구하면 다시 올게!

TextEng: Hold on, what about a reward?
You wait, girly. Me want reward.
Here, take the snow globe.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> This snow globe is pretty valuable to you. I think you could spare some coin for its return.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 이 스노 글로브가 당신에게 꽤 가치 있을 거예요. 돌려드리는 대가로 금화를 좀 주실 수 있을 것 같은데요.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> This be worth lots for you. Me think maybe you give some gold for me give it you.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 이거 너한테 가치 많아. 나 생각엔 아마 내가 이거 주면 너 금화 좀 줘야 해.

TextEng: Deal.
Forget it.
It's gone!
Snowball be gone!
Tell me where I can find the snow globe again.
Text: 스노 글로브를 어디서 찾을 수 있는지 다시 말해주세요.

TextEng: You say where me look for snowball again, 'kay?
Text: 눈덩이 어디서 찾는지 다시 말해줘, 알았지?

TextEng: I've changed my mind. Get me inside the snow globe.
Text: 마음을 바꿨어요. 스노 글로브 안으로 넣어주세요.

TextEng: Me change mind. Me want get inside snowball.
Text: 나 마음 바꿨어. 나 눈덩이 안으로 들어가고 싶어.

TextEng: Who are you, again?
Who you be, again?
You're drunk!
You be drunk!
I need to find the Words of Power.
Me need to find Power Words.
I'll be going now.
Me go now.
What are you talking about?
What you talk about?
Goodbye.
How do I get into the snow globe?
How me get into snowball?
I don't have time to look for your snow globe. I need to find the Words of Power right now!
Text: 당신 스노 글로브 찾을 시간 없어요. 지금 당장 권능의 언령을 찾아야 한다고요!

TextEng: Me not got time for look for you snowball! Me got find Words of Power fast!
Text: 나 네 눈덩이 찾을 시간 없어! 나 권능의 언령 빨리 찾아야 해!

TextEng: I can't waste my time looking for a snow globe!
Text: 스노 글로브 찾느라 시간 낭비할 수 없어요!

TextEng: Me not waste time looking for some snowball!
Text: 나 눈덩이 찾느라 시간 낭비 안 해!

TextEng: You're nothing more than a common grave robber!
You nothing but a grave robber!
But how did you end up working for Aarin Gend?
Text: 하지만 어떻게 아린 겐드를 위해 일하게 됐어요?

TextEng: But how you be working for Gend?
Text: 하지만 어떻게 겐드 위해 일하게 됐어?

TextEng: Goodbye.
You tell me what you know 'bout Power Words.
Text: 권능의 언령에 대해 아는 거 말해줘.

TextEng: What can you tell me about the Words of Power?
Text: 권능의 언령에 대해 뭘 말해주실 수 있나요?

TextEng: Hmmm... me think maybe me should get you another drink so you pass out and not bother me no more.
Text: 흠... 나 생각엔 아마 내가 술 한 잔 더 사서 네가 정신 잃고 날 더 이상 귀찮게 안 하게 만들어야 할 것 같아.

TextEng: Maybe I should get you another drink so you'll pass out and quit your drunken babbling.
Text: 술 한 잔 더 사서 정신 잃고 취한 헛소리 그만하게 만들어야겠네요.

TextEng: Me think you had too much booze, lady.
Text: 나 생각엔 너 술 너무 많이 마신 것 같아, 아가씨.

TextEng: I think you've had enough to drink, Lillian.
